  "detailed_description": "An incredibly beautiful and charming third-person journey, where every corner of this world hides amazing stories awaiting their explorers. Do you want to know what awaits you in this magical place?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/f23730436380ca52bbee288dae6e4d96.poster.avif?t=1722848623\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/f23730436380ca52bbee288dae6e4d96.webm?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/f23730436380ca52bbee288dae6e4d96.mp4?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>The game has three biomes to explore, each with unique gameplay mechanics, rich with beautiful, stunning landscapes and puzzles.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/5df47550cb626971b8348b66840aed04.poster.avif?t=1722848623\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/5df47550cb626971b8348b66840aed04.webm?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/5df47550cb626971b8348b66840aed04.mp4?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>This game is about heaven. You will embark on an exciting adventure where you need to help our adorable, little friends - dogs - find their way to paradise.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/71e3fce2f226f63b0dc89ba3139bdbf1.poster.avif?t=1722848623\" width=616 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/71e3fce2f226f63b0dc89ba3139bdbf1.webm?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/71e3fce2f226f63b0dc89ba3139bdbf1.mp4?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Offerings play a main role in the game progress. They unlock access to additional bonuses that help you solve previously inaccessible puzzles and visit secret places.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/dbdd8687b43b56070bdb7eb9f1ec93f1.poster.avif?t=1722848623\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/dbdd8687b43b56070bdb7eb9f1ec93f1.webm?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/dbdd8687b43b56070bdb7eb9f1ec93f1.mp4?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>How to solve puzzles is up to you! Each character has unique and common game mechanics, which gives you freedom of choice in how you solve them.</i><br><br><i>You and Max are in for an amazing adventure - share this special time together until the end.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/e8c5659d05b6d2b95b6540ab06b1a9c3.poster.avif?t=1722848623\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/e8c5659d05b6d2b95b6540ab06b1a9c3.webm?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><i>Music by:</i> <strong>Scott Buckley</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "An incredibly beautiful and charming third-person journey, where every corner of this world hides amazing stories awaiting their explorers. Do you want to know what awaits you in this magical place?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/f23730436380ca52bbee288dae6e4d96.poster.avif?t=1722848623\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/f23730436380ca52bbee288dae6e4d96.webm?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/f23730436380ca52bbee288dae6e4d96.mp4?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>The game has three biomes to explore, each with unique gameplay mechanics, rich with beautiful, stunning landscapes and puzzles.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/5df47550cb626971b8348b66840aed04.poster.avif?t=1722848623\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/5df47550cb626971b8348b66840aed04.webm?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/5df47550cb626971b8348b66840aed04.mp4?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>This game is about heaven. You will embark on an exciting adventure where you need to help our adorable, little friends - dogs - find their way to paradise.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/71e3fce2f226f63b0dc89ba3139bdbf1.poster.avif?t=1722848623\" width=616 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/71e3fce2f226f63b0dc89ba3139bdbf1.webm?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/71e3fce2f226f63b0dc89ba3139bdbf1.mp4?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Offerings play a main role in the game progress. They unlock access to additional bonuses that help you solve previously inaccessible puzzles and visit secret places.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/dbdd8687b43b56070bdb7eb9f1ec93f1.poster.avif?t=1722848623\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/dbdd8687b43b56070bdb7eb9f1ec93f1.webm?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/dbdd8687b43b56070bdb7eb9f1ec93f1.mp4?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>How to solve puzzles is up to you! Each character has unique and common game mechanics, which gives you freedom of choice in how you solve them.</i><br><br><i>You and Max are in for an amazing adventure - share this special time together until the end.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/e8c5659d05b6d2b95b6540ab06b1a9c3.poster.avif?t=1722848623\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435920/extras/e8c5659d05b6d2b95b6540ab06b1a9c3.webm?t=1722848623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><i>Music by:</i> 